Name: CVE-2014-1201
Description: Buffer overflow in the INetViewX ActiveX control in the Lorex Edge LH310 and Edge+ LH320 series with firmware 7-35-28-1B26E, Edge2 LH330 series with firmware 11.17.38-33_1D97A, and Edge3 LH340 series with firmware 11.19.85_1FE3A allows remote attackers to cause a denial of service (crash) and possibly execute arbitrary code via a long string in the HTTP_PORT parameter.

Name: CVE-2014-1203

Name: CVE-2014-1209
Description: VMware vSphere Client 4.0, 4.1, 5.0 before Update 3, and 5.1 before Update 2 does not properly validate updates to Client files, which allows remote attackers to trigger the downloading and execution of an arbitrary program via unspecified vectors.

Name: CVE-2014-1213
Description: Sophos Anti-Virus engine (SAVi) before 3.50.1, as used in VDL 4.97G 9.7.x before 9.7.9, 10.0.x before 10.0.11, and 10.3.x before 10.3.1 does not set an ACL for certain global and session objects, which allows local users to bypass anti-virus protection, cause a denial of service (resource consumption, CPU consumption, and eventual crash) or spoof "ready for update" messages by performing certain operations on mutexes or events including (1) DataUpdateRequest, (2) MmfMutexSAV-****, (3) MmfMutexSAV-Info, (4) ReadyForUpdateSAV-****, (5) ReadyForUpdateSAV-Info, (6) SAV-****, (7) SAV-Info, (8) StateChange, (9) SuspendedSAV-****, (10) SuspendedSAV-Info, (11) UpdateComplete, (12) UpdateMutex, (13) UpdateRequest, or (14) SophosALMonSessionInstance, as demonstrated by triggering a ReadyForUpdateSAV event and modifying the UpdateComplete, UpdateMutex, and UpdateRequest objects.
References: BID:65286   |   URL:http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/65286   |   BUGTRAQ:20140131 CVE-2014-1213 - Denial of Service in Sophos Anti Virus   |   URL:http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/530915/100/0/threaded   |   CONFIRM:http://www.sophos.com/en-us/support/knowledgebase/2300/7200/1031/120401.aspx   |   FULLDISC:20140131 CVE-2014-1213 - Denial of Service in Sophos Anti Virus   |   URL:http://seclists.org/fulldisclosure/2014/Feb/1   |   MISC:http://packetstormsecurity.com/files/125024/Sophos-Anti-Virus-Denial-Of-Service.html   |   MISC:http://www.portcullis-security.com/security-research-and-downloads/security-advisories/cve-2014-1213/   |   OSVDB:102762   |   URL:http://osvdb.org/102762   |   SECTRACK:1029713   |   URL:http://www.securitytracker.com/id/1029713
